n Kats (co-produced by Sonic Acts) and Maia Urstad on Ràdio Web MACBA, and ‘Send and Receive’: a podcast with Maia Urstad, Eva Rowson and Anton Kats on Lighthouse, in which they discuss their different ways of working with radio as tools for communication, programming and listening.CONDITIONS : 1218-0719 is a collaborative release co-produced by Bergen Kunsthall (Norway), Lighthouse (United Kingdom), Sonic Acts and Paradiso (Netherlands). Part of Re-Imagine Europe, co-funded by the Creative Europe Programme of the European Union.","headline":"MÆKUR's CONDITIONS : 1218-0719 now available as limited edition vinyl","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://2020.sonicacts.com/images/_1200x630_crop_center-center_82_none/Mækur_cover_final.jpg?mtime=1581344303"},"inLanguage":"en-gb","mainEntityOfPage":"https://2020.sonicacts.com/news/mækur-release-conditions-1218-0719-as-part-of-sonic-acts-academy-2020","name":"MÆKUR's CONDITIONS : 1218-0719 now available as limited edition vinyl","publisher":{"@id":"#creator"},"url":"https://2020.sonicacts.com/news/mækur-release-conditions-1218-0719-as-part-of-sonic-acts-academy-2020"},{"@id":"#identity","@type":"LocalBusiness","name":"Sonic Acts","priceRange":"$"},{"@id":"#creator","@type":"Organization"},{"@type":"BreadcrumbList","description":"Breadcrumbs list","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","item":"https://2020.sonicacts.com/","name":"Front Page","position":1},{"@type":"ListItem","item":"https://2020.sonicacts.com/news/mækur-release-conditions-1218-0719-as-part-of-sonic-acts-academy-2020","name":"MÆKUR's CONDITIONS : 1218-0719 now available as limited edition vinyl","position":2}],"name":"Breadcrumbs"}]}</script></body>

